column5: See the link below, there is alot of ice out there, I guess we won't be getting as much snow squalls for the rest of the winter even if it does get cold.  Georgian Bay  Rob C
Looking at the weather, it's going to start getting warm. All it takes is a couple rainy days and the ice will be gone, goes a lot faster than it forms.
Don't let that shot fool you. There's lots of open water on Georgian Bay...lake Huron and all the ice you see in this shot is now piled on Wasaga Beach after Mondays 90 K winds.!
Got lots of drinkin to do there Mr. Clampet?!!!!!   Rob C
